         <div type="translation">
            <ab>The 12th year of Aurelius Antoninus Caesar the lord Armeniacus Medicus Parthicus Germanicus Maximus, Pachon 16th for the account of Pharmouthi. Aretion, apator, his mother being Thermouth() has paid for poll tax of the eleventh year, Treasuries' quarter, twenty drachmas, that is 20 (dr.), extra ten obols.</ab>
